document.topic_text: HBO movie-ah J.Lo chang dawn Zaithiam, movie-ah pawh kan hmuh fo Jennifer Lopez chu movie dangah a chang leh dawn. HBO-in movie an tih­chhuah tur, The Cocaine Godmother-ah J.Lo hi a chang dawn a, a chan tur hi kum 1970 chho, 1980 chho vel thlenga US-a ruihhlo tawlhruk lamah hmeichhe turu, Griselda Blanco lem a ni. J.Lo hi tunah hian NBC crime drama series, Shades of Blue-ah a chang mek bawk. Share this Post
